  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever wondered if the dinosaurs really went extinct because of a meteorite? Or perhaps, just maybe, they were defending themselves against cunning players like you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting tower defense game, your mission is simple: defend your base from waves of dinosaurs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Turrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/9f60f6404e0c863cea3c3929e363dc5a.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/9f60f6404e0c863cea3c3929e363dc5a.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Set up powerful turrets strategically to blast away incoming dinos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Turrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/39f056c7236040dc00ec4aaaa626018c.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/39f056c7236040dc00ec4aaaa626018c.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Each type of turret can be upgraded, enhancing both its effectiveness and appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Resources</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/7476720b8dc67e9e8aa6875b00b8eb84.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/7476720b8dc67e9e8aa6875b00b8eb84.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Keep a close eye on your resources to build and upgrade defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft Strategies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/b7d2210a67a35de7851cf27159c8ced3.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/b7d2210a67a35de7851cf27159c8ced3.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Combine different turret types to create crazy strategies. Experiment with a variety of turrets, each with unique abilities and characteristics. Develop innovative tactics by mixing and matching turrets to adapt to every situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for fast-paced action and intense dinosaur battles in Jurassic Tower Defense!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever wondered if the dinosaurs really went extinct because of a meteorite? Or perhaps, just maybe, they were defending themselves against cunning players like you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting tower defense game, your mission is simple: defend your base from waves of dinosaurs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Turrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/9f60f6404e0c863cea3c3929e363dc5a.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/9f60f6404e0c863cea3c3929e363dc5a.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Set up powerful turrets strategically to blast away incoming dinos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Turrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/39f056c7236040dc00ec4aaaa626018c.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/39f056c7236040dc00ec4aaaa626018c.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Each type of turret can be upgraded, enhancing both its effectiveness and appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Resources</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/7476720b8dc67e9e8aa6875b00b8eb84.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/7476720b8dc67e9e8aa6875b00b8eb84.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Keep a close eye on your resources to build and upgrade defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft Strategies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras/b7d2210a67a35de7851cf27159c8ced3.avif?t=1742500177\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981910/extras_big/b7d2210a67a35de7851cf27159c8ced3.avif?t=1742500177 width=800 height=450 /></span>Combine different turret types to create crazy strategies. Experiment with a variety of turrets, each with unique abilities and characteristics. Develop innovative tactics by mixing and matching turrets to adapt to every situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for fast-paced action and intense dinosaur battles in Jurassic Tower Defense!</p>",
